[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    616[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m "This is the patient-safety signal that matters. An adverse event happened and the detector did not flag. The on-call clinical-informatics team reviews these same-day." On the [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mmissed_adverse_event[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m metric: names the false-negative-is-the-failure-mode framing from the main recipe.[K
